{
  "texts": [
    "Responses were scored for fluency (i.e., number of responses), originality (i.e., uniqueness of responses), and elaboration (i.e., number of words per valid response).",
    "Participants were given 3 min to generate their responses for each item.",
    "Following prior research 40, instructions for human respondents on the AUT were:",
    "For this task, you'll be asked to come up with as many original and creative uses for [item] as you can.",
    "The goal is to come up with creative ideas, which are ideas that strike people as clever, unusual, interesting, uncommon, humorous, innovative, or different."
  ]
}